  "title": "Site Supervisor | Cable work | Start Immediate | Up to $7k",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Cable Work Site Supervisor</strong></u><br /><br />Salary: SGD 3,500 – 7,000 (based on experience and certifications obtained)<br />Working Days: 6 days per week<br />Working Hours: 8 hours per day<br /></p><p><br /><u><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li>To maintain and monitor project deadlines as per the work schedule </li><li>To supervise and ensure works are in accordance to the contract drawings and specifications. </li><li>Ensuring adherence to health and safety regulations at all times. </li><li>Site planning, coordination with workers, scheduling and support to Project Manager </li><li>Regular monitoring of project progress and reporting to Project Manager </li><li>Liaising with Main / sub-contractor and attending site meeting. </li><li>Carry out site inspection </li><li>Co-ordinate and monitor the availability and on time delivery of materials / equipment to complete the construction work within schedule. </li><li>Resolve worksite issue effectively in order to keep work progress on track. </li><li>Staying up to date with safety codes and advancements in construction. </li><li>Any other ad hoc task from superior or management. </li></ul><p><br /><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Experience in civil, electrical, or utility construction (preferably power cable projects).</li><li>Ability to read and understand construction drawings, especially cable route and section drawings.</li><li>Familiarity with SP Group, LTA, PUB, or similar regulatory requirements is an advantage.</li><li>Strong communication and coordination skills.</li><li>Basic safety knowledge and willingness to follow WSH requirements.</li><li>Certifications such as BCSS, PSM, WSQ Safety Supervisor, or Work at Height.</li><li>MHA clearance done is an advantage. </li></ul><p><br /><strong>Chin Racheal (R25157940)</strong><br /><strong>Business Edge Personnel Services (96C4864)</strong></p>",
